title: Mug, 1820–30
description: Beaker form, sides flared towards top; cut with 3 arched panels filled with strawberry diamonds and blazes, band of flat fluting and raised ring with blazes below; thick foot cut with vertical fluting sides and straw- berry diamonds; notched loop handle.

tombstone.epitaph:
Mug, 1820–30.
1820–30. glass. Bequest of Walter Phelps Warren. 1986-61-89.
